The paper focuses on the development and testing of intelligent visual systems, specifically in the context of Visual Question Answering (VQA) task. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also introduces a new interactive learning framework, which involves asking questions, indicating that it may also be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing and understanding, which suggests that it may also be relevant to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
